<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbefaed71-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s9858a"><num value="9858a">§ 9858a.</num><heading> Establishment of block grant program</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is authorized to make grants to States in accordance with the provisions of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbefaed72-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/35/tVI/s658C">Pub. L. 97–35, title VI, § 658C</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/101/508/tV/s5082/2">Pub. L. 101–508, title V, § 5082(2)</ref>, <date date="1990-11-05">Nov. 5, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/1388-236">104 Stat. 1388–236</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/102/401/s3/a">Pub. L. 102–401, § 3(a)</ref>, <date date="1992-10-07">Oct. 7, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/1959">106 Stat. 1959</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/102/586/s8/c/1">Pub. L. 102–586, § 8(c)(1)</ref>, <date date="1992-11-04">Nov. 4, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/5036">106 Stat. 5036</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
