<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbefaed75-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1992—<ref href="/us/pl/102/401">Pub. L. 102–401</ref> and <ref href="/us/pl/102/586">Pub. L. 102–586</ref> made identical technical corrections to directory language of <ref href="/us/pl/101/508/s5082/2">Pub. L. 101–508, § 5082(2)</ref>, which added this section.</p>
